query:
SELECT team, COUNT(*) as player_count, SUM(overall) as total_overall,
       (SUM(overall) - 1098) as over_cap
FROM players 
WHERE team IS NOT NULL AND team != 'Free Agents' AND team != 'Free Agent'
GROUP BY team 
HAVING SUM(overall) > 1098
ORDER BY total_overall DESC
